query:
SELECT userId, eventId, COUNT(*) as count, GROUP_CONCAT(id ORDER BY enrolledAt DESC) as enrollment_ids
FROM course_enrollments
GROUP BY userId, eventId
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
ORDER BY count DESC;
